# HTML/CSS Standards for CCTV Malang

## HTML Structure
- Use semantic HTML5 elements
- Include proper meta tags for viewport and charset
- Use Indonesian language attribute (lang="id")
- Structure content logically with proper headings
- Include accessibility attributes (alt, aria-label, etc.)

## CSS Organization
- Use CSS Grid and Flexbox for layouts
- Implement responsive design with mobile-first approach
- Use CSS custom properties for consistent theming
- Group related styles together
- Use meaningful class names with BEM methodology when appropriate

## Design System
- Primary colors: #667eea (blue), #764ba2 (purple)
- Status colors: #28a745 (online), #dc3545 (offline)
- Use consistent spacing scale (8px, 16px, 24px, 32px)
- Use Segoe UI font family for consistency
- Implement glassmorphism effects with backdrop-filter

## Responsive Breakpoints
- Mobile: < 768px
- Tablet: 768px - 1024px  
- Desktop: > 1024px

## Component Patterns
- Use consistent button styles with hover effects
- Implement loading states with spinners
- Use modal patterns for detailed information
- Create reusable popup components
- Implement proper focus management

## Performance Considerations
- Minimize CSS specificity conflicts
- Use transform and opacity for animations
- Implement CSS containment where possible
- Use will-change property sparingly
- Optimize images and use appropriate formats

## Accessibility
- Ensure sufficient color contrast ratios
- Implement keyboard navigation support
- Use proper heading hierarchy
- Include focus indicators
- Provide alternative text for images

## Example CSS Structure
```css
/* Component base */
.component-name {
    /* Layout properties */
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    
    /* Spacing */
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 8px 0;
    
    /* Visual properties */
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    
    /* Transitions */
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

/* Component states */
.component-name:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}

.component-name.active {
    /* Active state styles */
}

/* Responsive adjustments */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .component-name {
        padding: 12px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
    }
}
```